TITLE: Configuring i18n Integration in Nuxt Config
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to configure the integration between @sit-onyx/nuxt and @nuxtjs/i18n modules. The example defines locales and sets up a mapping for Onyx's built-in translations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/schwarzit/onyx/blob/main/apps/docs/src/development/packages/nuxt.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
export default defineNuxtConfig({
  modules: ["@sit-onyx/nuxt", "@nuxtjs/i18n"],
  i18n: {
    defaultLocale: "en_US",
    locales: [
      { code: "en_US", file: "en-US.json", name: "English (US)" },
      { code: "de", file: "de-DE.json", name: "Deutsch" },
    ],
  },
  onyx: {
    i18n: {
      registerLocales: {
        "de-DE": "de-DE",
        en_US: "en-US",
      },
    },
  },
});
```

