TITLE: Creating Storybook Preview with createPreview Utility
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the createPreview utility in Storybook's preview.ts file to configure enhanced features for Onyx components. This setup includes improved controls, Vue code highlighting, dark mode support, and custom theming.
SOURCE: https://github.com/schwarzit/onyx/blob/main/apps/docs/src/development/packages/storybook-utils.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
